<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SQL Injection Demo - Security Learning Lab</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ee7752 0%, #e73c7e 50%, #23a6d5 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .navbar {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 15px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    .navbar a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .navbar a:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
    .container {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .form-container {
      background: white;
      padding: 50px 40px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      max-width: 450px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      color: #999;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .warning {
      background: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffc107;
      border-left: 5px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #856404;
    }
    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    input[type="text"],
    input[type="email"],
    input[type="password"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #ee7752;
    }
    button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ee7752 0%, #e73c7e 50%, #23a6d5 100%);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(238, 119, 82, 0.4);
    }
    button:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .error {
      background: #f8d7da;
      color: #721c24;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-left: 5px solid #f5c6cb;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .success {
      background: #d4edda;
      color: #155724;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-left: 5px solid #c3e6cb;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .demo-section {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .demo-section h3 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .demo-section p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .demo-section code {
      background: white;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      color: #d32f2f;
      display: block;
      margin: 8px 0;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      word-break: break-all;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .links {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .links a {
      color: #ee7752;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .links a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .info-box {
      background: #e3f2fd;
      border-left: 5px solid #2196F3;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #1565c0;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .form-container {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="/">‚Üê Security Learning Lab</a>
    <div>
      <a href="/login" style="margin-right: 20px;">Login</a>
      <a href="/search">Search</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="form-container">
      <h1>üíâ SQL Injection Demo</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Halaman Login yang Vulnerable</p>

      <div class="warning">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è WARNING:</strong> Halaman ini sengaja dibuat vulnerable untuk tujuan pembelajaran. Jangan coba di website real!
      </div>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <% if (success) { %>
        <div class="success"><strong>‚úì Sukses!</strong> <%= success %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/login">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email Address</label>
          <input type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="masukkan email..." required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="password">Password</label>
          <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="masukkan password...">
        </div>
        <button type="submit">Login</button>
      </form>

      <div class="demo-section">
        <h3>üîì Cara Eksploitasi SQL Injection:</h3>
        <p><strong>1. Masukkan di field Email:</strong></p>
        <code>' OR 1=1 --</code>
        <p><strong>2. Kosongkan atau isi password apapun</strong></p>
        <p><strong>3. Klik Login</strong></p>
        <p>Anda akan berhasil login karena query menjadi: <code>SELECT * FROM users WHERE email = '' OR 1=1 --' AND password = '...'</code></p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong>User Valid untuk Testing:</strong><br>
          Email: admin@example.com<br>
          Password: admin123
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="links">
        <a href="/search">Ke XSS Demo ‚Üí</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
